---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy | Fastbooks";
const description = "Privacy policy for Fastbooks prelaunch early access.";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} source="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="section page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Last updated: June 3, 2026</p>
  </section>
  <section class="section-soft">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="card" style="display: grid; gap: 24px; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>Welcome to Fastbooks. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting the information you share with us during our private early access prelaunch phase.</p>
        
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you request early access to Fastbooks, you may choose to provide certain details such as your name, company name, mobile phone number, email ID, and a brief description of your accounting needs. This information is collected directly when you initiate a chat with us on WhatsApp or submit the optional details form.</p>
        
        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>The information we collect is used solely to evaluate early access requests, communicate with you regarding waitlist status, and gather feedback to improve Fastbooks. We do not sell, rent, or lease your information to third parties.</p>
        
        <h2>4. Data Storage and Redirection</h2>
        <p>This website is a static site and does not host a persistent database. When you submit details via the waitlist form, the data is structured into a text format and redirected directly to our official WhatsApp account. We do not store your credentials or files on this web server.</p>
        
        <h2>5. Consent and Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>By clicking "Request Early Access" or messaging us, you consent to communicate via WhatsApp, which is a third-party service governed by its own privacy terms. We advise you to review WhatsApp's privacy policy before sharing sensitive business records.</p>
        
        <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to have your contact information removed from our list, please contact us directly via our primary WhatsApp link or email.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
